						<p>The Contribution for each BoatDay will be displayed to a Guest on each Listing before the Guest sends a participation request to a Host. As noted above, the Host is required to either confirm or reject the participation request within the Participation Request Period, otherwise the participation request will be automatically cancelled. If a participation request is cancelled or rejected (i.e. not confirmed by the applicable Host), any amounts collected by Peer to Pier (or its third party payment processor) will be refunded to such Guest, and any pre-authorization of such Guest&rsquo;s credit card will be released, if applicable.</p>
